M 4 README

Game requirements:
 - It is possible to start a new game by pressing r.
 - There are 14 I/O connections on the game.
 - There are two types of enemies: ground enemies which are killed using grenades and air enemies which are killed by shooting them.
 - There are buttons on the wall that revert the gravity.
 - All objects are being drawn using sprites.
 - All movable entities (player and enemies) use animated sprites.
 - There are two boxes which can be broken using grenades.

Approximate hours: 12 hours
